ast= Garner |first= Richard |date=2013-12-26 |title= Teachers threaten more strikes as talks with Michael Gove stumble |trans_title=教师威胁更多的罢工作为与迈克尔·戈夫的谈判失败的回应 |url= http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/teachers-threaten-more-strikes-as-talks-with-michael-gove-stumble-9026340.html |newspaper=The Independent |accessdate=2014-03-27}}</ref>2014年3月发生了影响1万所学校的罢工行动。<ref>{{Cite news |last= Saul |first= Heather |date=2014-03-26 |title= Teachers' strike affects 10,000 schools |trans_title=教师的罢工影响了10000所学校 |url= http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/teachers-strike-affects-10000-schools-9216018.html |newspaper=The Independent |accessdate=2014-03-27}}</ref>

