在他上任后的三个月内，刑事律师协会认为他们工作报酬较低而投票决定停止接受新业务，抗议戈夫。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Bowcott |first=Owen |date=2015-07-15 |title= Barristers vote to join solicitors' legal aid protest |trans_title= 大律师投票加入律师的法律援助抗议 |url= https://www.theguardian.com/law/2015/jul/15/barristers-vote-to-join-solicitors-legal-aid-protest |newspaper=The Guardian |accessdate=2015-07-16}}</ref>刑事律师协会还称赞他不再坚持提议削减法律援助的“勇气”。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Barrett |first1=David |title=Legal aid cuts reversed by Justice Secretary Michael Gove |trans_title= 司法大臣迈克尔·戈夫恢复了法律援助|url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/12128011/Legal-aid-cuts-reversed-by-Justice-Secretary-Michael-Gove.html |accessdate=2016-01-28 |work=The Daily Telegraph |location= London |date=2016-06-12}}</ref>2016年7月14日[[特蕾莎·梅|特蕾莎·梅]]首相上台后，戈夫不再担任司法大臣。<ref name="sacking" />

