== 宗教观点 ==
2012年，戈夫在[[威斯敏斯特公学|威斯敏斯特公学]]对学生们说“为自己是基督徒而自豪”。在[[老字号_(足球)|-{zh-hans:流浪者;zh-hk:格拉斯哥流浪;zh-tw:格拉斯哥流浪者;}-對-{zh-hans:凯尔特人; zh-tw:塞爾提克; zh-hk:些路迪;}-足球赛]]前演唱{{le|饥荒歌|Famine Song}}时，在场人们的“反天主教咆哮”引发关注，戈夫将苏格兰的弱势群体受到的保护归功于枢机主教[[凯斯·奥布莱恩|凯斯·奥布莱恩]]的智慧，同时对Kirk中没有类似的人物感到遗憾。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Gove |first=Michael |date=2008-11-01 |title=Flabby Kirk needs to regain its moral might |trans_title=Flabby Kirk需要重新获得它的道德力量 |url=http://www.scotsman.com/news/michael-gove-flabby-kirk-needs-to-regain-its-moral-might-1-1300849 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |newspaper= The Scotsman |location= Edinburgh}}</ref>

戈夫支持向[[英格兰|英格兰]]和[[威尔士|威尔士]]的所有学校提供[[钦定版圣经|-{詹姆士}-王译本]]（扉页题写“教育大臣敬献”）以纪念该书出版400周年，他说他支持这个计划是因为其中的历史和文化意义，而不是纯粹的宗教理由。<ref name=Indy-kjb>{{Cite news |last= Hughes |first= David |date=2012-05-25 |title= Michael Gove defends school Bibles scheme |trans_title=迈克尔·戈维捍卫学校圣经计划 |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/michael-gove-defends-school-bibles-scheme-7788925.html |accessdate=2013-10-27 |newspaper=The Independent |location=London}}</ref><ref name=guardiankingjames>{{cite news |last=Wintour |first=Patrick |date=2012-01-17 |title=And lo! Gove's Bible project did run into a spot of bother |trans_title= 戈夫的圣经项目遇到麻烦|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2012/jan/17/michael-gove-king-james-bible |accessdate=2013-10-27 |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London}}</ref>

== 私人生活 ==
戈夫与[[Sarah_Vine|Sarah Vine]]结婚，她曾在《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》工作，<ref>{{cite web |title= Michael Gove |trans_title= 迈克尔·戈夫 |url= http://www.conservatives.com/People/Members_of_Parliament/Gove_Michael.aspx |accessdate= 2013-10-27 |publisher= [[Conservative_Party_(UK)|Conservative Party (UK)]] |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131106054026/http://www.conservatives.com/People/Members_of_Parliament/Gove_Michael.aspx |archive-date= 2013-11-06 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>2013年成为《[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]》专栏作家。<ref>{{Cite news |title= Gove defends newspapers' 'right to offend' in Miliband row |trans_title=戈夫反驳报纸上米利班德的“权利侵犯”行为 |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-24363765 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |publisher=BBC News |date=2013-10-02}}</ref> 2009年《新政治家》杂志预估戈夫的家产为100百万英镑左右。<ref>{{Cite news |first1= Samira |last1= Shackle |first2= Stephanie |last2= Hegarty |first3= George |last3= Eaton |date= 2009-10-01 |title= The new ruling class |trans_title= 新统治阶层 |url= http://www.newstatesman.com/uk-politics/2009/10/oxford-universitywealth-school |accessdate= 2013-10-27 |newspaper= New Statesman |archive-date= 2009-10-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091004124121/http://www.newstatesman.com/uk-politics/2009/10/oxford-universitywealth-school |dead-url= no }}</ref>戈夫是[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部]]的支持者。<ref>{{cite news |last=White |first=Michael |author-link=Michael White (journalist) |date=2014-05-19 |title=Diary: Match of the day? Wembley's all set for a Michael Gove-Jeremy Browne love-in |trans_title=日记：一天的比赛？温布利球场所有的座位见证迈克尔·戈夫和杰里米·布朗的激情 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/may/19/diary-michael-white-wembley-qpr-derby |newspaper=The Guardian |access-date=2016-04-04 |archive-date=2016-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414101310/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/may/19/diary-michael-white-wembley-qpr-derby |dead-url=no }}</ref>

